  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    AlreadyIsAClosedDayException
    Exception that happens when there is an attempt to add a closed day that already is a closed day
    DayHasPassedException
    Exception that happens when a client attempts to schedule a trip to a date that has passed
    DoesntExistReservationFromClientException
    Exception that happens when the client does not have the reservation that is being removed
    EmailAlreadyExistsException
    Exception that happens when a user tries to register with an email that already exists
    FlightDoesntExistException
    Exception that happens when a flight does not exist
    NoNoticesException
    Exception that happens when there is no notice to show
    NotAClosedDayException
    Exception that happens when trying to remove a closed day that isn't a closed day
    NotAnEmailException
    Exception that happens when an email has an invalid format
    OnlyClosedDaysException
    Exception that happens when there are only closed days between a time range
    ReservationDoesntExistException
    Exception that happens when a reservation doesn't exist

    Exception that happens when the flight is unavailable
